--- TESTCASE Get Company By Id - Success - 200 OK

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [200]
## TEST-HAS-BODY
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{CompaniesSection}}/{{CompanyId}}

--- TEST
await tp.Test("Response should match the previously created company.", async () =>
{
    dynamic body = await tp.Response.GetBodyAsExpandoAsync();
    NotNull(body);
    NotNull(body.id);
    Equal("Software Company", (string)body.name);
    Equal("SWCOMP", (string)body.code);
    Null(body.managerId);
});

--- END


--- TESTCASE Get Company By Id - Nonexistent Company - 404 Not Found

--- HTTP
## TEST-EXPECT-STATUS: [404]
GET {{ApiBaseUrl}}{{CompaniesSection}}/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

--- END
